DATA SOURCE ATTRIBUTIONS

Trust Atlas incorporates data from multiple sources, each with their own
licensing terms. See docs/DATA_SOURCES.md for full attribution requirements.

Key sources include:
- World Values Survey (Custom Terms - non-commercial academic use)
- European Social Survey (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)
- Transparency International CPI (CC BY 4.0)
- World Bank WGI (CC BY 4.0)
- V-Dem (CC BY-SA 4.0)
- General Social Survey (Public Domain)
- ANES (CC0)
- And others documented in DATA_SOURCES.md

This license (CC BY-SA 4.0) was chosen to be compatible with V-Dem's
ShareAlike requirement while maximizing reusability.
